完，供淨6成，都肯提供長過10年少少按揭<br />\n<br />\n但25年樓以上，好似無咩銀行肯做<br />\n<br />\n未補價居屋買家資格受限，<br />\n銀行因此對高齡未補價居屋按揭生意興趣麻麻"},{"pid":"c1db1c58d35f01d7459ec697d3392dcc4d5d79af","tid":145293,"uid":49588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T08:36:10.000Z","msg":"我身邊有人買了過30年的居屋，現在供緊bor!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcdd1194c68fcd897160a88ba1dd6197e83ad6d5","tid":145293,"uid":27568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T08:47:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔買啦，公屋我當2000一個月，租100年都只係2,400,000 仲唔洗夾大維修</blockquote><br />\nagger</blockquote><br />\n免管理費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n免租<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最慘俾民X聯旗下d 人圍標搞大維修<br />\n用晒法團d 錢<br />\n戶戶幾十萬咁款"},{"pid":"906d1d25539d673a9654b9f34dfc88553f920d42","tid":145293,"uid":56244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T08:56:42.000Z","msg":"我係過來人, 幾年前綠表買居二, 借9成既話, 供款年期真係會用樓齡去計, 點計就唔知..我果到23年樓, 最後批到13年供款.   但果陣仲有第二個方法, 就係只係7成, 咁供款期可以比到25年"},{"pid":"f0d3732efba0395d3c2d68293b18537d0850f5a5","tid":145293,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T09:02:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我身邊有人買了過30年的居屋，現在供緊bor!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n補左地價既居屋=私樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  買果陣有做壓測"},{"pid":"a04667239e6633d279a796e7cc20636188408f79","tid":145293,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T09:16:56.000Z","msg":"信唔過政府，買居屋等仆街，除非永遠自住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57b7a987e5c99dffd2bfa085cb1f64b788d1c869","tid":145293,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T13:46:16.000Z","msg":"lm"}]}